      • toPattern

        @Nullable
public static @Nullable java.lang.String toPattern(java.lang.CharSequence date)
        Guesses and returns pattern of given date string. It can match these pattern:
        • 20111203: yyyyMMdd
        • 10:15:30: HH:mm:ss
        • 2011-12-03: yyyy-MM-dd
        • 2011-12-03+01:00: yyyy-MM-ddZZZZZ
        • 2011-12-03 +0100: yyyy-MM-dd ZZZ
        • 10:15: HH:mm
        • 10:15:30.500: HH:mm:ss.SSS
        • 10:15:30+01:00: HH:mm:ssZZZZZ
        • 10:15:30 +0100: HH:mm:ss ZZZ
        • 2011-12-03T10:15:30: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss
        • 2011-12-03 10:15:30: PATTERN_SECOND
        • 2011-12-03T10:15:30+01:00: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ssZZZZZ
        • 2011-12-03T10:15:30 +0100: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss ZZZ
        • 2011-12-03 10:15:30 +0100: yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss ZZZ
        • 2011-12-03T10:15:30Z: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ssX
        • 2011-12-03 10:15:30.500: PATTERN
        • 2011-12-03 10:15:30.500 +0100: PATTERN_OFFSET
        Return null if no matched pattern.
        Parameters:
        date - date string
        Returns:
        pattern string or null
